#: tutorial.kolf:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Tutorial Course"
msgstr "Výučbový kurz"

#: tutorial.kolf:68
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Welcome</h3> to the tutorial course for Kolf!"
msgstr "<h3>Vítajte</h3> vo výučbovom kurze pre Kolf!"

#: tutorial.kolf:124
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold the Down Arrow or left mouse button. How "
"long you hold down the mouse button or key determines strength of the shot."
msgstr ""
"Aby ste udreli do lopty, stlačte a podržte šípku nadol alebo ľavé tlačidlo "
"myši. Ako dlho podržíte tlačidlo myši alebo kláves určuje silu úderu."

#: tutorial.kolf:180
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"To aim the putter, press the Left (rotate counterclockwise) and Right "
"(rotate clockwise) Arrow keys or use the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Aby ste zamerali golfovou palicou, stlačte ľavú (otáčanie proti smeru "
"hodinových ručičiek) a pravú (otáčanie v smere hodinových ručičiek) šípku "
"alebo použite myš."

#: tutorial.kolf:289
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Bridges</h3>Bridges can have walls on the top, bottom, left, or right."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Mostíky</h3>Mostíky môžu mať steny na hornej, dolnej, ľavej alebo pravej "
"strane."

#: tutorial.kolf:411
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Everything</h3>Here's a hole that has it all. Have fun with Kolf!"
"<br><center>-- Jason Katz-Brown</center>"
msgstr ""
"<h3>Všetko</h3>Tu je diera, ktorá má všetko. Bavte sa s Kolf!<br><center>-- "
"Jason Katz-Brown</center>"

#: tutorial.kolf:524
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Slopes</h3>Slopes are slanted areas of ground that push the ball in the "
"direction that they slope. This direction is shown when you choose <u>Hole-"
">Show Info</u>."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Naklonenia</h3>Slopes sú šikmé plochy terénu, ktoré tlačia loptu v smere "
"sklonu. Tento smer sa zobrazí, keď zvolíte <u>Diera->Ukázať Info</u>."

#: tutorial.kolf:579
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Hit the ball onto the slope and let it roll into cup."
msgstr "Udrie loptu smerom do naklonenia a nechať ju skotúľať sa do šálky."

#: tutorial.kolf:654
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Try out these different types of slopes."
msgstr "Skúste tieto rôzne typy sklonov."

#: tutorial.kolf:793
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"The steepness of a slope is shown when you choose <u>Hole->Show Info</u>. "
"Steepness goes from 8 (steepest) to 1 (shallowest)."
msgstr ""
"Strmosť naklonenia je zobrazené, ak zvolíte <u>Diera->Ukázať Info</u>. "
"Strmosť ide od 8 (najstrmšie) po 1 (najplytšie)."

#: tutorial.kolf:876
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Walls</h3>Bounce the ball off of the red walls."
msgstr "<h3>Steny</h3>Odraziť loptu mimo červených stien."

#: tutorial.kolf:985
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Sand</h3>Sand is yellow, and slows your ball down."
msgstr "<h3>Piesok</h3>Piesok je žltý, a spomaľuje vašu loptičku."

#: tutorial.kolf:1040
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Puddles (Water)</h3>Hitting into a puddle (blue) adds a penalty stroke "
"to your score, and your ball is placed outside the puddle."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Mláky (Voda)</h3>Zasiahnutie kaluže (modrá) pridáva trestný úder na vaše "
"skóre a vaša lopta sa umiestni mimo mláky."

#: tutorial.kolf:1111
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Windmills</h3>Windmills (brown base with moving arm) have brown walls "
"(or half walls). The speed of the windmill arm may vary for each hole."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Veterné mlyny</h3>Veterné mlyny (hnedá základňa s pohyblivým ramenom) má "
"hnedé steny (alebo polovicu stien). Rýchlosť veterného mlyna sa môžu líšiť "
"pre každú dieru."

#: tutorial.kolf:1194
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Black Holes</h3>Black Holes transport the ball to their exit, and eject "
"it at a speed in direct relation to the speed your ball was traveling. "
"Choose <u>Hole->Show Info</u> to see which Black Hole goes to which exit and "
"the direction the ball will come out."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Čierne diery</h3>Čierne diery dopravia loptu k ich východu a vyhodia ju "
"rýchlosťou v priamom vzťahu k rýchlosti, ktorou sa lopta pohybovala. Zvoľte "
"<u>Diera->Ukázať Info</u>, aby ste videli, ktorá čierna diera ide do ktorého "
"východu a smer, ktorým loptu vyjde von."

#: tutorial.kolf:1280
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Floaters</h3>Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands "
"on it. Floaters' speeds vary."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Plťky</h3>Plťky sú pohybujúce sa plošiny, ktoré nesú loptu, ktorá "
"pristane na nich. Plťky sa rútia rôzne."
